#

Slow Cooker Pork Tenderloin with Vegetables

495 min
$25
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freedairy-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

slow cookercomfort foodeasy meal

Description

A tender and juicy pork tenderloin slow-cooked with a medley of vegetables for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 2 pounds
  • carrots: 3 medium, sliced
  • potatoes: 4 medium, diced
  • onion: 1 large, chopped
  • garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • chicken broth: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1 teaspoon
  • rosemary: 1 teaspoon
  • thyme: 1 teaspoon
